articles.title: Post Game Report - Division 5: Leprechauns v Rock Lobsters
articles.content:
Division 5 - Rock Lobsters was beaten by Leprechauns 1 - 4. For Leprechauns, Phil Cazes pitched in with 22 Saves. Smally Small tallied 1 Goal, 1 Point. Scott Bangay wowed the crowd with 1 Goal, 1 Point. Yury Madyarov broke out 1 Assist, 1 Point. Andrew Phan managed 1 Goal, 1 Point. For Rock Lobsters, Jesse Fry scored 32 Saves. Adrian Whitham pitched in with 1 Goal, 1 Point. Visit the game page at: http://icehq.hockeysyte.com/game/6023

Catch the Replay on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xfDHaawVKIc
